{"tid":503883,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱返返下工無啦啦入廁所喊到仆街","createTime":"2017-12-19T10:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T18:51:26.000Z","uid":72054,"like":1792,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"d09e86a64b66e1c258604f151ca7feb86d79dd9e","tid":503883,"uid":72054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"我返緊pt sales，今日我婆婆入左黎買野 跟住我覺得自己好似好耐無見佢 見佢行路好似好唔順 要拖住行，之後買完野 佢去左對面samsung行 見佢睇野要靠到好埋先睇到，跟住我個心突然好酸 唸返起我又就生日 代表又少啲時間對佢 眼淚就隨之流出黎 之後仲跑埋去廁所喊 覺得自己無盡到做孫既責任 佢仲要塞錢比我洗 我真係喊到仆街 <br />\n比女飛定dse衰左 定係點唔如意好 我都未喊過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 一路喊一路打篇文<br />\n我唔敢想像有日訓醒 佢離開左我 我會喊成點 <br />\nSorry for 1999 純粹覺得打完心情會好過少少"},{"pid":"e6dee5987ca8521c50c0c40194caf05e20de5944","tid":503883,"uid":72054,"like":582,"dislike":6,"score":576,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:32:49.000Z","msg":"即刻約佢飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5845df063cf5c0982ebf4364d38edbd6702e21f6","tid":503883,"uid":107660,"like":248,"dislike":4,"score":244,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:41:07.000Z","msg":"真心有時間嘅，就好見下老人家"},{"pid":"393118ddbdfafd8c250ad36a812f1a2f7bf4500a","tid":503883,"uid":35746,"like":5,"dislike":36,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"不孝孫"},{"pid":"2fa8b4a17b3cfbda67882a5028317d1bc995026c","tid":503883,"uid":5419,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"唔使喊，錫多d你婆婆咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a446f20960ea6c1b6b74b653c5b39b9f3b396bf","tid":503883,"uid":122619,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"趁佢仲係到好好珍惜你婆婆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef67ffd89662169cab958abd50488829ff83e64","tid":503883,"uid":123456,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:50:42.000Z","msg":"巴打cheer up<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b29a321a7b7bf42d0b460d6366817c156a62146","tid":503883,"uid":8171,"like":168,"dislike":8,"score":160,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:51:44.000Z","msg":"樹慾靜而風不息 子慾養而親不在<br />\n多啲陪下老人家啦"},{"pid":"28eefcbafb1aa16121ed044602be90723ec0b8e6","tid":503883,"uid":75692,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:34:12.000Z","msg":"喊出黎啦<br />\n你喊完會舒服D<br />\n唔好諗太多 做好自己<br />\n好多野你控制唔到"},{"pid":"a1fa19639b7a32c768459545b31276cd086ea719","tid":503883,"uid":128850,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:36:06.000Z","msg":"要多啲陪下佢老人家<br />\n唔好俾自己後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043d526ef5358593eaa28cc2977adf20c8d95872","tid":503883,"uid":134563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"多啲陪返佢去飲茶食飯啦 有心唔怕遲"},{"pid":"3bfbcae626bb58499f4ea1066348b341b4b5106f","tid":503883,"uid":19858,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"我阿爺都90，我而家直頭想日日陪"},{"pid":"f07eb62f66d4186594383f1473e174be7f46dc35","tid":503883,"uid":162653,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T14:04:54.000Z","msg":"我都成日會唸呢啲跟住就會係咁喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實真係好愛佢地 好想自己可以成日陪住佢地<br />\n見住佢地有白頭髮 睇醫生密左 真係好心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可以做嘅只有孝順 同真係陪多啲佢地 用行動表達"},{"pid":"e0ba7d88d1ee423bc9d645364f8a573a89190655","tid":503883,"uid":119065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T14:27:06.000Z","msg":"驚世文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連仔齊來珍惜婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852d4b11e8ca9bdfd81051994d3dd87a4b4aff02","tid":503883,"uid":72054,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T14:31:09.000Z","msg":"都唔知自己無啦啦喊乜7 個客都呆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed90f37f42de0abd3f52817ca4832a6eeb7eb52","tid":503883,"uid":108978,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"諗起自己過左生既婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c3bcc2c2b1b7f79992fee019c69c49d4cf0b08","tid":503883,"uid":125873,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"好掛住我婆婆 <br />\n我知道你在遠處一直守護住我💓<br />\n<br />\n有次搭凌晨機無聊睇相 <br />\n睇見張佢老人家無咗一邊眼珠笑住同我自拍<br />\n即刻喊到收唔到聲.....腫住落機<br />\n<br />\n多啲搵佢老人家 佢唔似得你有好多朋友嘻嘻哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b06366ca25f4483dc3adc1bc61b85a10d4dad84","tid":503883,"uid":162377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"返工加油，賺錢同婆婆飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766c210e0bf2ebc0596ebf22decb166bb5f18fc9","tid":503883,"uid":109086,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"真係要好好珍惜佢<br />\n我由細到大都係得公公一個<br />\n其他係我出世之前都死哂<br />\n我仲好記得每一次我去見公公<br />\n一見面佢就會係咁笑<br />\n依家我終於明白點解佢會係咁笑<br />\n由於我地唔同地區關係 有時1年都未必見到一次面<br />\n因為好耐無見過自己個孫開心到由心到笑出黎<br />\n雖然每次見面時間唔長 但每一晚我地都會傾好耐計<br />\n佢已經走左好多年 到依家我仲好清楚記得佢對住我笑果陣既開心樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d4b7d34fab28b1bd79fe52d5094f8dd1ee2235","tid":503883,"uid":129335,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"我阿麻由我細細個養到我大，所以我一直最孝順佢。如果我係你就多陪佢飲茶，因為佢想要既只係想見下你，其他咩都唔洗佢就可以好開心。<br />\n<br />\n成日自己係到唸有日佢走左我會喊成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21e48db0cc61e3f538c139afec5c74897c47456","tid":503883,"uid":63768,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:13:59.000Z","msg":"我婆婆已經走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唸返起以前真係好on9。總之唔好俾自己後悔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2e63b71e8f5cde52308588c234a644d1332e28","tid":503883,"uid":44403,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"如果呢件事令你有反思同成長，令你更珍惜同婆婆嘅關係，咁絕對係一件好事，用行動表達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a6b84b888cf6c8da1fa9084f1ebfcb3f748643","tid":503883,"uid":6457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我婆婆已經走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唸返起以前真係好on9。總之唔好俾自己後悔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be19e7ba0297a969e90a08683c0b93336e00dcf","tid":503883,"uid":127451,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"細細個我係啊爺湊大，但係我細個好百厭成日激佢，後來我小學個陣佢就過左身。到大個左，聽返以前d街坊講起我啊爺點樣照顧我，加上睇返d 舊照，就會好掛住佢。"},{"pid":"9d40da92f8ee2984b70085edb32b5af4510abf6c","tid":503883,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"大個仔la<br />\n祝你出人頭地"},{"pid":"54f2b7dd14c52f2a20c012a3125fba9069d7f090","tid":503883,"uid":76135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"樓豬孝仔心. 珍惜每一天."},{"pid":"0a6ccf578277d9da7a59860732fedebafa563a72","tid":503883,"uid":65563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"我公公婆婆喺我幾歲時候已離開我，但我對佢地記憶好深，到而家都記得佢地好錫我，記得佢地把聲，記得佢地同我講嘅嘢，<br />\n同佢地嘅合照永遠都喺我床頭，每晚都會對住張相，內心同佢地心靈交流，我信佢地一直仲喺某個地方睇住我。<br />\n<br />\n我最遺憾當時太細個無能力去照顧佢地，而家大個女唯有對屋企人更加好，更努力去照顧佢地。<br />\n<br />\n我男朋友公公婆婆80幾歲，公公就行得走得，婆婆就好容易唔舒服（男朋友話婆婆幾年前曾經大病入院，醫生話好危險，但婆婆又好叻咁，最後都無事出院），佢地都好錫我，我亦當正佢地喺我公公婆婆一樣，同男朋友一個月會去離島幾次過夜幾日，陪佢地飲下茶，周圍行下，煮下飯佢地食。<br />\n<br />\n我眼中呢老人家好可愛，特別喺佢地講以前嘅嘢同埋叫我地夾多啲餸食嗰陣，我覺得好warm，好sweet。<br />\n<br />\n對於仲可以成日有機會見既人，要好好珍惜，多啲關心佢地，時間唔等人，亦有好多意外嘅事情自己估計唔到，放多啲時間同愛俾對方，我諗大家都會好幸福。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0609e6d408cc7fd892d6fc334777fb65838e4573","tid":503883,"uid":20544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"珍惜阿樓主<br />\n我都係細細個比爺爺嫲嫲湊大<br />\n佢地都好錫我<br />\n當我慢慢懂事<br />\n佢地就已經離開佐我<br />\n果隻切膚之痛真係成世都唔會忘記<br />\n個心真係喊到痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣係到諗點解人要擁有感情<br />\n正因為了解咩係愛<br />\n所以離別先特別痛<br />\n但係我宜家係到諗<br />\n佢地既岀現令到我擁有一個被愛既童年<br />\n即使最後會痛苦<br />\n但佢地係無可取代<br />\n自問對佢地都算好<br />\n但一諗起佢地仍然會痛⋯⋯<br />\n所以老土都講句<br />\n唔好比自己後悔<br />\n成為一個佢地都會為你自豪既乖孫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2370c6b8877daa48a9c5621b0a983d5739dcaf","tid":503883,"uid":120729,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"睇呢個post睇到喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ed817488d0bb6ade30996ffaa6849928dfb5b1","tid":503883,"uid":49363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392fe67257a9c780e12c43aefc3b70fdeaf100cd","tid":503883,"uid":21262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"婆婆仲健在 每次一夾到時間都會陪佢打牌食飯 每次打電話俾佢佢都笑出聲 聽到佢笑我就好開心 雖然我唔知佢因咩笑得咁開心 佢80歲啦就黎 好想佢長命百歲睇到我結婚生個曾孫俾佢"},{"pid":"97d51dbb506916c982c8e282a4007b9941418791","tid":503883,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:01:50.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"ffefba988e8d6902feb2bed08b8d6e0eaf7a56b2","tid":503883,"uid":91546,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"樓主 在生的時候 同佢飲多兩次茶 <br />\n人死左就咩都冇嫁<br />\n幾風光大葬都唔代表d咩<br />\n你第時幾有錢 燒幾多野都唔及今日陪佢飲的一餐茶<br />\n你搵到錢 請佢飲茶 帶俾佢地個種開心 佢地真係到臨死個刻都仲記得<br />\n利申： 呀爺 呀麻 公公 婆婆 都過身了"},{"pid":"79a8e41a84ff660f4f8ad756b2f3f9b2ee38b47e","tid":503883,"uid":83706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"而家知道唔算遲<br />\n不過你唔好掛住喊<br />\n你而家係要諗樣去對佢好啲同行動<br />\n等自己唔好有遺憾"},{"pid":"9957c7ee68a1573d1481f912d682281172a58bea","tid":503883,"uid":76472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:07:17.000Z","msg":"細細個都係婆婆湊大<br />\n仲記得以前起酒樓食飯太攰瞓咗<br />\n都係婆婆搵件外套笠住我 又搵多張凳比我瞓<br />\n仲成日買野比我食<br />\n依加大個咗就好少見 一年見得2-3次左右<br />\n其實我真係想像唔到呀婆死果陣我會喊成點<br />\n真係太殘忍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打呢段野果陣已經喊到隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b042f54ababbd2c52f8b5438e7b3601a7f44e9","tid":503883,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"我婆婆走個陣我都趕唔切去見佢最後一面<br />\n巴打你要珍惜"},{"pid":"d1dcf48e452988f11e3e6fc0a733c148b4766094","tid":503883,"uid":72054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:17:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得大家睇到個po名會以為等笑新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45de50c3e8ae04ac54df7021b8e53e6522cb859e","tid":503883,"uid":143657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:23:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ecf157d62e58a6b09b846a5dd3733d8e2052640","tid":503883,"uid":158741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"陪佢地多d 啦～"},{"pid":"29490748a6d972ca457ec3b1093195ad1ec35b9c","tid":503883,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:28:30.000Z","msg":"Never too late"},{"pid":"5620717d0282d7fe73ecc4ccc2f6fc5556daa08e","tid":503883,"uid":7203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:29:59.000Z","msg":"學其他巴打話濟 有時間就陪下佢地啦 星期日唔洗番工的話2/3個鐘去陪佢地飲茶或者求其出去食餐飯啦"},{"pid":"f724097057aeb36b70079f2b51db5a7c1dd3e627","tid":503883,"uid":138803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:32:26.000Z","msg":"多啲陪佢，已經好好<br />\n<br />\n我已經再冇機會同任何grandparents見面，樓主好好珍惜啦"},{"pid":"fac62e4087d64034a8aa19859046f631ca7c40c4","tid":503883,"uid":104446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:34:22.000Z","msg":"老人家走真係好傷心<br />\n尤其由細湊大你個啲"},{"pid":"705053c431266d0da62a9a477e650f2a4d1e946d","tid":503883,"uid":6573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"我都係阿婆湊大<br />\n依家大個左都係大時大節先見到佢<br />\n我諗佢第時真係走左我諗我會喊到停唔到"},{"pid":"cd4d1033d808b943ace79499a0d5134f3a304168","tid":503883,"uid":103394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:39:01.000Z","msg":"唉 好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6910af7d26ddda3dd6a223135e3e8a0d591cc424","tid":503883,"uid":154896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"抽啲時間見下老人家，買下生果，陪佢飲下茶，佢地已經覺得你乖仔又開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31e282dff395e3f38364ee7889e21c2b9d77f47","tid":503883,"uid":62239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個post好催淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 睇其他巴絲打講既嘢真係睇到眼濕濕<br />\n點都好 都係嗰句 &ldquo;珍惜眼前人&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好把握同佢哋相處既時間<br />\n有時真係好話唔好聽<br />\n今日唔知聽日事<br />\n所以呢 心動不如行動<br />\n多d見下佢哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3d55d41484d9c18531831d4723d64d19a7aa57","tid":503883,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:45:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WZTGUh7V_mk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWZTGUh7V_mk&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2FppZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=6c06368f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WZTGUh7V_mk</a><br />\n愛得太遲"},{"pid":"9b8987bf6a16df8e6235edfbc77ad0444c1b7b19","tid":503883,"uid":49176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"我都係婆婆湊大<br />\n以前都試過無啦啦諗如果婆婆走左點算<br />\n一諗到就會喊<br />\n但我唔明你生日同少d 時間有咩關係"},{"pid":"f0ced355fcb75b80083facfa6da77467b5a46a44","tid":503883,"uid":72054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係婆婆湊大<br />\n以前都試過無啦啦諗如果婆婆走左點算<br />\n一諗到就會喊<br />\n但我唔明你生日同少d 時間有咩關係</blockquote><br />\n發覺咁快又到生日 姐係好似又少左時間咁"},{"pid":"cdf12e787522101d20574d813449bbb3d9e571ea","tid":503883,"uid":52984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:51:49.000Z","msg":"珍惜!"},{"pid":"ee6f502e11d53020fc64027aa597c4252f2fd961","tid":503883,"uid":62379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"得閑就陪多啲屋企人啦，好好珍惜佢哋響你身邊嘅時間，因為錯過咗就冇得翻轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd3e5b9d8d4e5e069b44b45cea2197e92cd5ae1","tid":503883,"uid":62911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"婆婆今年過左身，先諗返自己原來係幾咁仆街。在生個時成日關心我，問我讀書讀成點返pt返得辛唔辛苦叫我比心機叫我加油，我都唔為意就咁應幾下就算，到佢真係離開左先諗識後悔，巴打唔好好似我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fc9531c4cb5d219d7172270c4b6302ea9fabaf","tid":503883,"uid":17351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣睇post睇到眼濕濕..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b517c9a35cfba69c7a0d885ec7c8daa64b8189c","tid":503883,"uid":4155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:00:47.000Z","msg":"老人家其實好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n趁有機會就愛錫佢地多啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3dde37dd92d5d30fa69c05a9da7b24ff674c46","tid":503883,"uid":67504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即刻約佢飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乖仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa63674c4223ffb0603c23c7f5d11a6af4af1417","tid":503883,"uid":74995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"講咁多有咩用，行動啦，好多野話唔埋，唔好等"},{"pid":"bdb073546f6c39a073c26d9f4d7b86b5662c3795","tid":503883,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:21:38.000Z","msg":"唉屌<br />\n睇完自己都差D係公司喊<br />\n對唔住我去左WORKING HOLIDAY我不孝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85bb71f7cc3f8d1859991b1d780318adaec1b41","tid":503883,"uid":33095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"100個正評"},{"pid":"b368aea71ec68369e489a6104398e02502e8c0e6","tid":503883,"uid":116250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:25:40.000Z","msg":"間唔中都會諗如果自己至親走咗自己會有幾失落幾無助 跟住就會喊 i know that feeling bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d171f6cdd42b843d1434bfff702819e36946a0","tid":503883,"uid":89236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"婆婆啱啱走左，一路睇po一路喊到仆街<br />\n好好珍惜啦，經過左呢次之後覺得好多野好無常好突然，當每次都係最後一次好好陪住佢<br />\n因為你唔會知邊次最後一次飲茶，最後一次拖佢，最後一次望住佢精精神神"},{"pid":"ce408b0860fada1fad8ac8d1395b1f6d6684ddc7","tid":503883,"uid":137489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:55:47.000Z","msg":"完全唔敢諗阿婆會走 阿媽之後最愛既人就係佢 雖然好on9 但我每次返去都會同佢一齊訓 等佢開心下 只希望阿婆可以身體健康就夠"},{"pid":"0b922bd41fd3ee416a3e5d0e2dabbd4d1857701f","tid":503883,"uid":106018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"以前嫲嫲好鍾意捉住我隻手 係咁摸 果時岩岩大個仔 有啲反感<br />\n然後佢成日都叫我帶個女朋友比佢睇  又叫我第時大個要請佢飲茶..<br />\n<br />\n點知無一樣做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bb22ad9901138c113e10a3b638d2687275494c","tid":503883,"uid":25025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T19:00:28.000Z","msg":"呀婆湊大我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日出去拎報紙，想幫補家計，但其實屋企雖然窮，但都唔係無錢開飯<br />\n有一日，佢朝早去拎完，成日都無返嚟<br />\n最後呀媽係醫院搵到佢，比的士佬撞咗<br />\n重記得我係醫院摸佢個頭，佢無張開眼，但係流咗眼淚出嚟。<br />\n過幾日佢死咗，好後悔返緊學無去睇佢最後一程<br />\n樓主珍惜吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd9a560a8737891d08cac1423a1af7511fc98ae","tid":503883,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T19:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樹慾靜而風不息 子慾養而親不在<br />\n多啲陪下老人家啦</blockquote><br />\n欲"},{"pid":"5d922423f50b8f5d5764953f9fcbbb8ad2ec519a","tid":503883,"uid":38188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T19:55:41.000Z","msg":"仲識後悔同補救係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267d8c4bd1c1e9847a86ee3c06325494080eead6","tid":503883,"uid":139124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T20:19:17.000Z","msg":"陪多啲佢啦"},{"pid":"2b9c803032e6426d3e0a1ec7ad5986ad59d4c065","tid":503883,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"